1 - Resume
~~~~~~~~~~

This is the Gopiler assembler.
This software is design to turn mips assembly code into text oriented 

2 - Usage :
~~~~~~~~~~~

Windows :
Just double click on start_gopiler.bat
The input used file is input.asm
The output file is ouput.txt
(Note that you can change thoses files by editing start_gopiler.bat)

Linux :
"./gopiler -h" will tell you everything you need !


3 - Supported instructions :
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

add
or
xor
sub
beq
sll
slr
lw
sw
slt
andi
ori
addi

label

and comments (start the line by a ;) of course !
